lead_paragraph: FIFA has denied a claim by the Bolivian football federation (FBF) that it has returned four World Cup qualifying points which were docked on Tuesday as punishment for fielding an ineligible player.

headline.print_headline: FIFA Denies Returning Four Points to Bolivia Over Ineligible Player
